Building and installing (requires gcc and make):

	make
	sudo make install

Running:

	sidreloc --help

Manual page:

	man sidreloc

Sidreloc is primarily a linux program, but it's open source (MIT license, see
the file "COPYING" for details) and you are encouraged to port it to different
operating systems. Good patches will be merged into the official version.

http://www.linusakesson.net/software/sidreloc/
